Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take my focus off of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what they're going through\Nright now, they'll survive for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I let you get away now,\Nyou'll go kill my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take my focus off of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really defeat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't protect anyone unless I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body. Empty Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was able to meet a man\Nwith some backbone. How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run out of strength from\Nyour doping earlier after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's backbone you want, I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...another tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third... Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power that moves\Nfrom one bone to another...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look! My left arm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the arm of a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all show, don't even bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shivering Past! Dark Justice and Rob Lucci"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm about to pass out.\NI can't fall into the sea like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and help the injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A beast?!\N--No, he's a power holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I landed on the deck of\Na battleship. That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He flew from the direction of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a huge hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous ahead of here!\NWater is rushing towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't you guys hear the sound of water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if the water flows into\Nan underground passage like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have no choice but to drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-kun, can't you hear the sound of water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it's true that\Nsomething doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stop, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other passage. We have\Nno choice but to keep on this path!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny and the others\Nare being chased by water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Do something about this water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something?! What're we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you! This passage is\Ngonna be flooded with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rushing into my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We're gonna be shut in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cut it! So this isn't iron or stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an undersea passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be made of some damn thick steel\Nthat can bear the water pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's nowhere to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't safe here! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good! The sea train won't start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any engineers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks will reach here soon! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do about capturing\NNico Robin on the Bridge of Hesitation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Leave her alone.\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as that man is on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is given the mission\Nof escorting Nico Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just burn everything down\Nexcept the Bridge of Hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this man you mentioned be...\NMr. Rob Lucci of CP9?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we suspected, he's a power holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're asking who you are! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is... Mr. Rob Lucci of CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rob Lucci-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! Please spare our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouths. Your whining hurts my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot about Mr. Rob Lucci,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he is really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was an incident where 500\Nsoldiers got captured by pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:41.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"15 years ago"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Don't hold back! Go wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill anyone who resists! Show no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flinch! Protect this\Ncountry from the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kingdom put up unrelenting\Nresistance against the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn pirates...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trench mortars...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for you! If you don't wanna die,\Njust give up and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist, we'll blow you away\Nwith these trench mortars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all our hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw them all in a warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for the hostages' lives,\Nthe pirate captain demanded the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty. For the sake of the citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should firmly refuse the\Npirates' despicable demand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of the kingdom's\Nmain military and the Imperial Guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have to fear those pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those soldiers who fought risking their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up being taken\Nhostage are also my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit back and let them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this throne is taken away,\Nit's possible to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't take back people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if we accepted the pirates' demands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to believe that they'd\Nrelease the hostages as they promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! An emissary from the\NWorld Government has just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?! From the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him in immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the kingdom that was about\Nto surrender with its hands tied
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over its concern for the hostages,\Nthe World Government sent a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That blasted World\NGovernment! How insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prey? You mean the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're occupying the western\Nharbor and making it their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'd like you to leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the highest priority\Nto the hostages' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell the\NWorld Government what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why does this boy make me so intimidated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat and drink to your heart's content\Nand have a good time tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kingdom ain't actually a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it ain't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the kingdom will be all ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! He's the new king!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booze! We're running out of booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us, too! Someone, bring some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's booze is especially tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You guys...\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the World Government,\NI've come to arrest you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest?! Me?! A brat like you will arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the Government\Nis really hard up for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:13:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can one little brat do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna pretend to be some\Ngovernment big shot, do it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it! We got no time\Nto play games with a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you who's gonna move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used a weird technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be a total lie that\Nyou're from the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do any more weird stuff,\Nwe can't guarantee the hostages' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you obey us,\Nwe'll keep you alive for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:14:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a hostage for the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now no one can defeat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw that brat in the same\Nlockup where the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have you stay in here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a "Great Emissary"\Nfrom the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he came to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Government will\Ndo whatever we tell them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can defeat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:15:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys are all hostages.\NTry and get along in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to verify one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all of the hostages here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the boy infiltrated the\Npirates' hideout, right then and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he killed all 500 of the kingdom's\Nsoldiers who were taken hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Killed all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be...! Is something like that permissible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:16:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's the World Government...\NEven if it's for justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Justice isn't all warm and fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, too, remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the pirates got\Nangry and rained bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,upon the boy who was standing on the\Nmountain of bodies with his back turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boy stood up in the flame of explosions,\Nkilled the boss of the pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and settled that incident all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss! Boss!...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down! What's the problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is going on a rampage in the lockup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... kill our important hostages...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They committed a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I executed them in the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soldiers of the kingdom,\Nbeing weak is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They surrendered to evil and\Nplunged the kingdom into a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers like that don't have the right to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! And you call yourself\Nan official of the World Government?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice would never surrender to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That serves you right, you damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat us like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! After all the trouble we\Nwent through, our plan got ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H... How could he have survived that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy, who had several\Nbullet marks on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a CP9 intelligence agent at the age of 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call him the strongest\Nand cruelest mass killing machine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the history of CP9,\Nwhose mission is dark justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he was capable of\Nall that when he was only 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why all we have\Nto do is fulfill our own duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Straw Hat Luffy, whose\Nbounty is 100 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd be that fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Pigeon guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work! The Bone Balloon is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Giant Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Is it a giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:20:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Giant Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The masts got broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're falling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight between those two is just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol...! Pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that as your power increases,\Nyour speed decreases.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick... Victory Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron outer shell got cracked...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close. I almost got split in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Cutty Flam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for you guys! Or rather,\Nit was all over from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit early to say that\Nwhen the fight isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who is fighting Straw Hat is Lucci.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the strongest man in the history of CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might've been able to\Nget rid of the others okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Lucci's another story entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Straw Hat is taken out,\Nyou're next, Cutty Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Give me a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Vice Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that Straw Hat Luffy and\NMr. Rob Lucci of CP9 are currently fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the #4 ship got wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rob Lucci isn't gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the gunners on all ships, aim at the #4 ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire all cannons together in five seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Vice Admiral, you must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand of our men are onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:22:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A moment's indecision can allow\Nvicious criminals to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you protect our future from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were finally able to free Robin-chan,\Nbut if we don't do anything, we'll drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe... I can't hold my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful... you are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Mystical Mermaid Appears?\NAs Consciousness Fades Away..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
